Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 Samekh复活的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后祭典的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Samekh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么巨大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类能拿它怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不来看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh并不是坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被我封印着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 和子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君回应了我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君已经不属于任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也不属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只须解开皆水封印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh到了零时空间外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君就会成为这颗星球上的王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球是须方君的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你期盼已久的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球上最后的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想利用素体成为世界支配者的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多么无意义 明白了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来你也只是个恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也是你可爱的地方 沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我为什么长久以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执着于这台素体Shinpathy（牙）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台Shinpathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有驯化素体的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 Samekh只能由进藤须方驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我能连同进藤须方和Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起据为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他会永远活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我操纵的Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的一个零件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把须方 还来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我的二刀流师出同门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个了结吗 Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh已经是我的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与现在的我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等同于和Samekh战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还未见识Samekh真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些巫女已经察觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚苏醒的Samekh饥饿难忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴求着复活所需的欲望能量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在发颤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的是零时空间的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开零时空间封印的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh为了成为原来的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吸干这颗星球的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那样做的话这颗星球会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Samekh的容量完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类灭亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭人类 得到Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又能怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除皆水封印 进入第五阶段的Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自由操纵时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为它的驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成为时间旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以无数次重复美好的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后的未来会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要夺回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙助先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被束缚着吗 时生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急动议！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德的行为违反绮罗星规约第11条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即除籍处分！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群极品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能迎来启程之日的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只是我用来取得Samekh的垫脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么绮罗星 傻不傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人的小屁孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志家的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水的素体？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然从神殿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正中我下怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了 Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh在我掌控中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你打坏了它们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所有素体都是Samekh的奴仆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Peshent（口）…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alephist（雄牛）…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是只属于我的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的梦即将开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来我们只是被利用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类染指素体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许对我们来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但素体是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们迟早会面对的可能性之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙妮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过这次的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德错误地使用了素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那台Samekh是台错误的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Daletos（门）在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的印记？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的印记复苏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yaddock（腕）…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tzadikt（纸莎草）…在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留有一丝辉光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉之鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 未能回归的素体们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑 纸吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团留下的乱摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挣脱Samekh的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发起行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢狱的看守者们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此巨大的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么巨大的东西 怎么才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为靠一腔热血能克服所有的这份年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在压倒性的力量面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然自己跳进Samekh本体放出的王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片青色的夜幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明自己的归宿和前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦碎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王之柱…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…要封印Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让Samekh沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说须方君是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为封印Samekh才驾驶的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 地球得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗有它的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅长表演被赋予的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自信一直保护和子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就这么打算的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的儿子和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见其他人看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底看见了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你我已经看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 须方还是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做的事和该做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一刹那 我也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 拓人君这么做是理所当然的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能放任须方那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从遇见你那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是给我们欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那或许才是你的第一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我最近常想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是 没有遇见你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没来到岛上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠都说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羡慕那些一心只想着心仪男子的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特别羡慕有了男朋友的琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此深深喜欢上两个男孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做也是徒劳 Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也别说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的家训
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们今后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会目睹比这更壮丽的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\blur3\bord6}人生的冒险还在继续
